-- Scotia Bank, Standard Chartered Approved for Membership on London Exchange
-- Claudia Carpenter
-- 2010-07-23T09:37:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-07-23/scotia-bank-standard-chartered-approved-for-membership-on-london-exchange.html

          
          
             Scotia Bank Europe and Standard
Chartered were approved to become associate broker clearing
members of the London Metal Exchange.  
 Their membership applications were approved by the board
yesterday, the exchange said in a statement e-mailed today.  
          
          


  


        